rows.label: tlk10030101_msg0002
rows.name:
Thought I was dead? I
thought I was dead too.

rows.label: tlk10030101_msg0003
rows.name:
Benkei told me, "I'm gonna beat you
up later, so don't you dare die."

rows.label: tlk10030101_msg0004
rows.name:
When she asks me like that, I can't
exactly just go and die, can I?

rows.label: tlk10030101_msg0005
rows.name:
Well then, I'm gonna go with you
to see the answer you found!
